&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years of product management experience, with ownership of complex consumer or marketplace experiences. Experience with AI or search experiences is helpful but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven &lt;strong&gt;zero‑to‑one&lt;/strong&gt; experience building new, user‑facing products or capabilities from early concept through launch and iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
